OL,7,FHayley John says she wants to share
OL,8,Fher story to give other people
OL,9,Fstrength, as ITV News Central's Peter
OL,10,FBearne reports
OL,12,FWarning: this article contains details
OL,13,Fthat some readers might find
OL,14,Fdistressing
OL,16,FA mother from Derbyshire says she is
OL,17,Fliving in fear after her abusive ex-
OL,18,Fpartner was released from prison,
OL,19,Fhaving served just a third of his
OL,20,Fsentence.
