OL,7,FHayley Johns's former partner Matthew
OL,8,FKowal was jailed for three years for
OL,9,Fcausing actual bodily harm and common
OL,10,Fassault.
OL,12,FHe was released after serving less
OL,13,Fthan three hundred days behind bars.
OL,15,FHayley from Little Eaton near Derby,
OL,16,Fsaid Kowal's abusive behaviour began
OL,17,Fjust months after they got together in
OL,18,FMay 2020.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
