OL,4,Cabusive ex-partner's early prison
OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FHayley said she confronted him on New
OL,8,FYear's Eve when she saw he had sent
OL,9,Fintimate pictures of himself to
OL,10,Fanother woman.
OL,12,FShe said: "He went from this
OL,13,Fbeautiful, lovely man to this monster.
OL,15,F"He strangled me, he threw me across
OL,16,Fthe bed, he shoved sex toys in my
OL,17,Fmouth to try to shut me up."
OL,19,FAfter that first incident, his abusive
OL,20,Fbehaviour "never really stopped."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
