OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FShe said: "It was everything I'd ever
OL,8,Fwanted, and I really really loved him.
OL,10,F"The beautiful side of him when I met
OL,11,Fhim was so infectious, but he could
OL,12,Fonly ever go a few months without
OL,13,Fcheating on me, physically and
OL,14,Fpsychologically abusing me.
OL,16,F"He would flip from being nice to
OL,17,Fbeing horrible; I was always walking
OL,18,Fon eggshells."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
