OL,7,FHayley described how she once tried to
OL,8,Fjump out of the window after Kowal
OL,9,Fbarricaded her in her bedroom, and
OL,10,Fsaid she wanted to end her life.
OL,12,F"As a victim you're just invisible"
OL,14,FHayley said despite the abuse she
OL,15,Fsuffered, she would have taken him
OL,16,Fback if he had taken accountability
OL,17,Ffor his actions.
