OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,F"To hear weeks after Christmas that
OL,8,Fhe's coming out, I hit the point where
OL,9,FI was very close to being hospitalised
OL,10,Ffor mental health.
OL,12,F"I felt as if I wasn't being heard,
OL,13,Fand as a victim you're just invisible.
OL,15,FHayley said she worries that when
OL,16,FKowal returns to Derby, he might seek
OL,17,Fher out.
